oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Forest Mill School
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of children at Forest Mill School on Fun Day. The teacher was Miss Wilma F. Brown (1910-1991). Some of the children are holding musical instruments. There is a dog and two puppies in the front row.
